name: Donny Dinero - Blue Plastic Statue
description:
Plastic pollutes and litters the world 
these days but there's something just 
so deliciously malleable about it. 
Our efforts to rid the world of it tends 
to be underwhelming to say the least. 
We, at KHC™, work on having virtual plastic 
become a delicacy of the future. 
We're bringing animated plastic to its 
highest calibre in order to assure ourselves 
ahead of the curve when the rest catch up.

Minimal in feature but majestic by sight!

Enjoy your very own Blue Plastic Statue now! 
Introducing COTC™'s mascot "Donny Dinero". 
In association with KHC™ Chemical & Tech.
Hold it tight and flaunt your virtual plastic 
assets to your peers of the future!
It's not just an investment, it's a life style.

Home made 3D design & animation.
Custom made analog VHS FX.
